        "descriptionHtml": "<p><strong>Note:</strong> Please refer to the following before installing the solution:</p>\n<p>• Review the solution <a href=\"https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/tree/master/Solutions/ZeroFoxAlerts/ReleaseNotes.md\">Release Notes</a></p>\n<p>• There may be <a href=\"https://aka.ms/sentinelsolutionsknownissues\">known issues</a> pertaining to this Solution, please refer to them before installing.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.zerofox.com/\">ZeroFox</a> solution for Microsoft Sentinel enables you to ingest <a href=\"https://www.zerofox.com/platform/\">ZeroFox Alerts</a> into Microsoft Sentinel using the ZeroFox API.</p>\n<p><strong>Underlying Microsoft Technologies used:</strong></p>\n<p>This solution takes a dependency on the following technologies, and some of these dependencies either may be in <a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/support/legal/preview-supplemental-terms/\">Preview</a> state or might result in additional ingestion or operational costs:</p>\n<ol type=\"a\">\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/azure-monitor/logs/data-collector-api\">Azure Monitor HTTP Data Collector API</a>)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Data Connectors:</strong> 1</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aka.ms/azuresentinel\">Learn more about Microsoft Sentinel</a> | <a href=\"https://aka.ms/azuresentinelsolutionsdoc\">Learn more about Solutions</a></p>\n",
